trans-unit.source: Specifies the visual state of a combo box that is drawn with visual styles.
trans-unit.target: Anger det visuella tillståndet i en kombinationsruta som ritas med visuella stilar.

trans-unit.source: The ComboBoxState values correspond to the states of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> objects exposed by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.ComboBox.DropDownButton> class.
trans-unit.target: ComboBoxState värden motsvarar tillstånd för <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement>objekt som exponeras av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.ComboBox.DropDownButton>klass.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.ComboBox.DropDownButton> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement>

trans-unit.source: The ComboBoxState values are also used as an argument in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBoxRenderer.DrawDropDownButton%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBoxRenderer.DrawTextBox%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods.
trans-unit.target: ComboBoxState värden används också som ett argument i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBoxRenderer.DrawDropDownButton%2A?displayProperty=fullName>och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBoxRenderer.DrawTextBox%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoder.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBoxRenderer.DrawTextBox%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBoxRenderer.DrawDropDownButton%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The combo box has the default appearance.
